RT @FEMA_Brock We appreciate Senator @marcorubio support as we begin Florida’s recovery. https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1052272613727367169 QT @marcorubio Takeaways from today’s Hurricane visits:
1. Housing a major need for foreseeable future;
2. Agriculture suffered severe loss &amp; will need help;
3. #FloridaPanhandle has some of the strongest communities in the U.S.;
3. #Florida has best disaster response system on earth. #Sayfie

